Arenaria 
<normalizedToken id="9FD6A3A2B58FC60AEFEF185F407F2FFA" originalValue="Marschlínsii" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Marschlinsii</normalizedToken>
Koch
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D862E3F526B40443320C4BB72A6AC643" pageId="null" pageNumber="824" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="FC58FD39C8322F6C1C946C0F2BBA222F" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Marschlins Sandkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="8462A10874149AB096EFE309810EA845" pageId="null" pageNumber="824" type="description">
<paragraph id="E25D8BC32BA18C03EF43BA4A7E216CB9" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
2-10 cm hoch. Stengel niederliegend oder aufsteigend. 
<emphasis id="7F1265C74A8BCB520256F0BCFFE92C51" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
Haare der 
<normalizedToken id="FCC2CC8B4FEEB0240DE4E2D09D528478" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="35776147271AE913E8D09B67E645AAED" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
0,2 bis 0,5 mm lang
</emphasis>
, oft 
<normalizedToken id="9F370D0B5F6374D58419197B99C4A605" originalValue="drüsig" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">druesig</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="1B950462AF74C8CF668C54BA3D3F8E75" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
1-2mal so lang wie breit. Fruchtstiele ⅔- 
<normalizedToken id="BB3676F075DDED4F4C7C11A3E875B403" originalValue="1½" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">11/2</normalizedToken>
mal so lang wie der Kelch. 
<emphasis id="A9474192A5CE6BFB341563D76A8396B1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
<normalizedToken id="45F86C08B4484909E60D13AF25F0862E" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
3,5-4 mm lang. 
<normalizedToken id="7283B527A737E44F79BBFA5022DA61A4" originalValue="Häutiger" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Haeutiger</normalizedToken>
Rand der innern 
<normalizedToken id="344DF30F5D258B446AE1CDC0DF9F6232" originalValue="Kelchblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Kelchblaetter</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="201996F38194B97696B5C4C7598A12A7" originalValue="½-¾" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">1/2-3/4</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="717936666728811EDCF2F089A07A974A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">so breit wie der krautige Mittelstreifen. Kapsel</emphasis>
zylindrisch bis 
<normalizedToken id="4DDD96452E2459C330F52838098730C8" originalValue="eiförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">eifoermig</normalizedToken>
, 
<emphasis id="75F755A232ED9F289E38E944BE047598" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">etwa 2mal so lang wie dick.</emphasis>
Samen 0,4 bis 0,7 mm lang. - 
<normalizedToken id="934F0157BD9A5EE822B09CE0F5831565" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="633D0B1250B9AF7F48E149D1A29F1A4D" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
<emphasis id="3BAFD91BC2D1AFAF1A9BD7CEBBC48415" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="C967E613835779695CCFAFF49230C98D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">20:</emphasis>
Material von 9 verschiedenen Stellen aus den Ostalpen (Griesinger 1937, v. Woess 1941).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="728DB26A090DC7BD03DAB410DADB44CF" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
<emphasis id="7BDF1B5B6D07CB75773E3CBA261DCF19" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Standort.</emphasis>
Alpin. Lockere, meist 
<normalizedToken id="E9C2859DA2D4AE548AA60C8F8423D958" originalValue="nährstoffreiche" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">naehrstoffreiche</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="19FA2C1E937B912709A6ED00FD9A1EBF" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="3DE8CD7F9E57651C52A4F784591DA6F0" originalValue="Lägerstellen" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Laegerstellen</normalizedToken>
, Ruhschutt, Grate.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="307CE517A7F2DD18C4C964205F4C2D8D" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
<emphasis id="9E3F96B4EC78D7ECB3F2149A709C2D4A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="19247678405F10AD2CFCF9C2C941BCC6" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="7D0B606E4756969B13E6DEAD40C823C5" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
(?), Alpen, Gebirge der Balkanhalbinsel. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen, Wallis, Aostatal, 
<normalizedToken id="FD1AA5BE6EA58A410CA11BCDAC3A8F9C" originalValue="nördliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">noerdliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin, 
<normalizedToken id="4D5EEF9F257CE1D32E8632344AED95E3" originalValue="Graubünden" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">Graubuenden</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="9F595A6AE2F082E0B9D55583CF4944B3" originalValue="südlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="824">suedlich</normalizedToken>
des Rheins), Veltlin, Vintschgau; selten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
